---
config:
  theme: neo-dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant R as Resident (Applicant)
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant D as DormSystem
    participant U as Resident
    participant B as Building
    participant RM as Room
    participant C as Contract

    Note over R,API: [1] Resident sends booking request
    R->>API: POST /request_booking(user_id, building_id, room_type)

    API->>D: request_booking(user_id, building_id, room_type)
    activate D

    Note over D,U: [2] Find resident
    D->>D: get_user_by_id(user_id)
    D-->>D: residentObj

    alt User not found
        D-->>API: LookupError ไม่พบรหัสผู้ใช้งาน
        API-->>R: HTTP 400 Error
    else User found
        
        Note over D,U: [3] Validate account status
        D->>U: get status
        U-->>D: AccountStatus

        alt Suspended or Pending
            D-->>API: PermissionError บัญชีอยู่ระหว่างการตรวจสอบ
            API-->>R: HTTP 403 Error
        else Account active
            
            Note over D: [4] Check office hours
            D->>D: check current time

            alt Outside office hours
                D-->>API: ValueError ขณะนี้อยู่นอกเวลาทำการ (08:00-17:00)
                API-->>R: HTTP 400 Error
            else Office hours valid
                
                Note over D,B: [5] Find building
                D->>D: get_building_by_id(building_id)
                D-->>D: buildingObj

                Note over B,RM: [6] Find and hold room
                D->>B: find_and_hold_available_room_by_type(room_type)
                activate B

                loop for each room in building
                    B->>RM: check_availability()
                    RM-->>B: boolean
                end

                alt No room available
                    B-->>D: LookupError ไม่พบห้องว่าง
                    D-->>API: error
                    API-->>R: HTTP 400 Error
                else Room found
                    
                    B->>RM: set status RESERVED
                    B->>RM: set hold_expiry +48h
                    B-->>D: roomObj
                    deactivate B

                    Note over D,C: [7] Create contract
                    D->>C: Contract(resident, room)
                    activate C
                    C->>C: generate contract_id
                    C-->>D: contractObj
                    deactivate C

                    D-->>API: contractObj
                    deactivate D

                    API-->>R: success response
                end
            end
        end
    end